<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<%- include ('../partials/head.ejs'); %>
	</head>

	<body>
		<header><%- include ('../partials/header.ejs'); %></header>
		<main>
			<div class="breadcrumbs">
				<a href="/">Home</a>/ <a href="/weeklynerd">Weekly Nerd</a>
			</div>

			<section class="regularcontent">
				<section>
					<h1>Weekly Nerd</h1>
					<p>
						Every week for the duration of the Web Design & Development minor, a
						guest from the workforce will give a guest lecture in the late
						Wednesday afternoon. These lectures cover a variety of subjects that
						can be (and usually are) of importance to 'rookie programmers' such
						as myself.<br />
						<br />
						In order to not lose the important knowledge I gain during these
						guest lectures, I've set up this <em>Weekly Nerd</em> blog - the
						very reason this site, in its entirety, exists. Let's discover the
						many interesting lessons learned during this semester at AUAS!
					</p>
				</section>
				<section class="featured">
					<h2>Hey, hello</h2>
					<p>
						This is a body text. This is a body text. This is a body text. This
						is a body text. This is a body text. This is a body text. This is a
						body text.
					</p>
				</section>
			</section>

			<section class="blogs">
				<h2>Blogs</h2>
				<p>
					An overview of the blogs written about the Weekly Nerds I've attended
					during the minor.
				</p>
				<section class="blog-grid">
					<% blogMetadata.forEach(metadata => { %>
					<article class="blog-item">
						<a href="/posts/<%- metadata.lecturerUrl %>" class="readblog">
							<div
								style="
									background-image: url('../images/<%- metadata.image %>');
								">
								<i class="material-symbols-outlined">arrow_outward</i>
							</div>
							<div class="card-info">
								<h5>On <%- metadata.date %></h5>
								<h3><%- metadata.name %></h3>
								<p><%- metadata.description %></p>
							</div>
							<h4 id="tagcontainer">
								<% metadata.tags.forEach(function(tag) { %>

								<span> <%- tag %> </span>

								<% }); %>
							</h4>
						</a>
					</article>
					<% }); -%>
				</section>
			</section>
		</main>
		<footer><%- include ('../partials/footer.ejs'); %></footer>
		<script src="/scripts/scrolltotop.js"></script>
	</body>
</html>
